<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="34" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1160,1653]" box="[151,1436,1237,1263]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,259,1237,1263]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Ecology:</emphasis>
— 
<materialsCitation box="[290,1432,1237,1263]" elevation="3930" location="Saxicolous" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:184887DA8025FFEF90C8FBEC1467B373:953E60178025FFEF917DFB0314A8B1E9" box="[290,416,1237,1263]" name="Saxicolous" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Saxicolous</location>
in shaded rock crevices and on cliffs; in central 
<collectingRegion box="[970,1073,1237,1263]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
in alpine vegetation at 
<quantity box="[1341,1432,1237,1263]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.9299999999999997" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" unit="m" value="3930.0">
<elevation box="[1341,1432,1237,1263]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.9299999999999997" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" unit="m" value="3930.0">3930 m</elevation>
</quantity>
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1160,1653]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,458,1276,1302]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Conservation status:</emphasis>
— 
<materialsCitation collectorName="de Perote" location="Cofre de Perote National Park" municipality="Cofre de Perote" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">
Critically Endangered (CR) B2ab(ii,iii) in 
<collectingRegion box="[998,1106,1276,1302]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
. Known from only a single specimen (AOO: 3.1 km 
<superScript attach="left" box="[452,460,1315,1329]" fontSize="6" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">2</superScript>
) made in 1958 at the eastern upper slope of 
<collectingMunicipality box="[1013,1205,1318,1344]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">
Cofre 
<collectorName box="[1091,1205,1318,1344]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">de Perote</collectorName>
</collectingMunicipality>
volcano in central 
<collectingRegion box="[151,261,1356,1382]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
, which is located within the 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:184887DA8025FFEF90C8FBEC1467B373:953E60178025FFEF9200FA9A16C3B060" box="[607,971,1356,1382]" municipality="Cofre de Perote" name="Cofre de Perote National Park" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Cofre de Perote National Park</location>
and thus somewhat protected, but still under high anthropogenic pressure. Specimens examined: 1; TK collections: 0
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1160,1653]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,266,1433,1459]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Note:</emphasis>
—The duplicate of this specimen at MEXU was identified in 1994 by ARS as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Smith &amp; Moran" authorityYear="1992" baseAuthorityName="Martens &amp; Galeotti" baseAuthorityYear="1842" box="[1212,1384,1434,1459]" class="Arachnida" family="Agelenidae" genus="Melpomene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pilosissima">
<emphasis box="[1212,1384,1434,1459]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">M. pilosissima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and cited in 
<bibRefCitation author="Mickel, J. T. &amp; Smith, A. R." box="[249,533,1472,1498]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" pagination="1 - 1054" refId="ref11253" refString="Mickel, J. T. &amp; Smith, A. R. (2004) The pteridophytes of Mexico. Memoirs of the New York Botanical Garden 88: 1 - 1054." type="journal article" year="2004">Mickel &amp; Smith (2004)</bibRefCitation>
as voucher for 
<collectingRegion box="[723,833,1472,1498]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
. However, the revision of that genus for the Flora Neotropica (M. Lehnert, pers. comm.) treated this specimen as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Smith &amp; Moran" authorityYear="1992" baseAuthorityName="Desvaux" baseAuthorityYear="1827" box="[890,1047,1511,1536]" class="Arachnida" family="Agelenidae" genus="Melpomene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="peruviana">
<emphasis box="[890,1047,1511,1536]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">M. peruviana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which thus is the first record for 
<collectingRegion box="[151,262,1550,1576]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
. 
<taxonomicName authority="(Mickel &amp; Beitel 1988: 205) Smith (1995: 21)" authorityName="Smith" authorityPageNumber="21" authorityYear="1995" baseAuthorityName="Mickel &amp; Beitel" baseAuthorityPageNumber="205" baseAuthorityYear="1988" box="[269,1079,1550,1576]" class="Arachnida" family="Agelenidae" genus="Melpomene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zempoaltepetlensis">
<emphasis box="[269,530,1550,1575]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">M. zempoaltepetlensis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Mickel, J. T. &amp; Beitel, J. M." box="[544,862,1550,1576]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" pagination="1 - 568" refId="ref11217" refString="Mickel, J. T. &amp; Beitel, J. M. (1988) Pteridophyte Flora of Oaxaca, Mexico. Memoirs of the New York Botanical Garden 46: 1 - 568." type="journal article" year="1988">Mickel &amp; Beitel 1988: 205</bibRefCitation>
) Smith (1995: 21)
</taxonomicName>
, as treated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Mickel, J. T. &amp; Smith, A. R." pageId="5" pageNumber="34" pagination="1 - 1054" refId="ref11253" refString="Mickel, J. T. &amp; Smith, A. R. (2004) The pteridophytes of Mexico. Memoirs of the New York Botanical Garden 88: 1 - 1054." type="journal article" year="2004">Mickel &amp; Smith (2004)</bibRefCitation>
, is a heterotypic synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Smith &amp; Moran" authorityYear="1992" baseAuthorityName="Desvaux" baseAuthorityYear="1827" box="[585,745,1588,1613]" class="Arachnida" family="Agelenidae" genus="Melpomene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="peruviana">
<emphasis box="[585,745,1588,1613]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">M. peruviana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
according to M. Lehnert (pers. comm.) and probably also occurs in 
<collectingRegion box="[265,363,1627,1653]" country="Mexico" name="Chiapas" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Chiapas</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
